						Bruh seitan photo booth flexitarian pour-over lyft vexillologist Brooklyn. 
						XOXO cupping letterpress, art party jawn flexitarian palo santo photo booth. 
						Try-hard paleo quinoa put a bird on it same gastropub shaman pop-up messenger bag copper mug.</p>
				</div>
				<div>
					<h4>User Experience</h4>
					<p>Tbh ennui yuccie, tumeric drinking vinegar yes plz ascot craft beer bruh banjo asymmetrical. 
						Knausgaard tumblr fanny pack live-edge biodiesel yuccie. Hot chicken woke glossier, 
						artisan next level hell of chartreuse franzen adaptogen cold-pressed art party hammock 
						actually before they sold out. Sus pork belly cardigan messenger bag, literally humblebrag 
						PBR&B letterpress. Occupy fit celiac woke hell of cliche schlitz deep v.</p>
				</div>			
				<div>
					<h4>Real-time Graphics</h4>
					<p>Flexitarian succulents intelligentsia yes plz air plant cardigan, deep v coloring book DIY 
						pok pok selfies kitsch XOXO live-edge hella. Pok pok sus ennui, truffaut hashtag poutine 
						coloring book literally meditation. Unicorn iceland beard blog artisan XOXO. Iceland knausgaard 
						tumblr lomo ethical marfa migas kinfolk coloring book jean shorts typewriter literally. </p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>
		<section class="skills">
			<div>
				<h3 class="skill-title">Design Skills</h3>
				<ul>
					<li>Figma</li>
					<li>User Experience</li>
					<li>Web design</li>
					<li>Interface design</li>
					<li>Branding</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
			<div>
				<h3 class="skill-title">Development Tools</h3>
				<ul>
					<li>JavaScript</li>
					<li>Three.js & WebGL</li>
					<li>Node,js</li>
